Dongguan Padmat Rubber Products Co., Ltd.(short name: Padmat Rubber) was founded in 2009.It is a laege private enterprise padmatwhich integrates R&D, manufacture and trade. Reader Interactions
Reviews
On Jul 23rd, 2022 Michael Whitener said
Every gun show is different I lived in Palm Beach FL. for 20yrs went to all the gun shows and they were different but it was for an area that supported a larger show, frankly, I think we are lucky to have the show we have I really appreciate the C&E they put on a good show. there are some vendors on some special weekends that want come soo if you don’t like it try it on another date you might find what your looking for as far as Hickory NC I wish they would come more often but I figure that politics play a roll in it. You can’t fix stupid
On Dec 11th, 2021 Evelyn Hayman said
We attend the Hickory Gun show and it’s well worth the trip and the entry fee. Lots of vendors and prices aren’t that bad either . Will be attending all events for 2022!
On Jun 29th, 2019 Mr. Willis said
Been going for 20 years. This has always been a great gun show. Ive been to several that were bigger but for variety hickory is always a good place to go. Aside from the usual booths there are usually nfa vendors, great miltaria collectiables, and antinque guns around. Where else can you buy pinfire revolvers and a 50 cal or 6.5 marksmanship rifles at the same show?
On Nov 2nd, 2017 Keith S said
I’ve been going for years. All I can say is, if you cant find it, you were not looking !
On Jul 21st, 2017 Michael Whitener said
Hey! I like it. It’s my belief is if you can find one better go to it don’t complain about your decision.
On Nov 4th, 2016 Don Vance said
This gun show is one of the best in this region. The vendors are all good folks. Besides guns, you can expect to see a variety of knives, along with other survival gear. If you are serious about what’s going on America, then you will want to attend this show to see what’s missing from your preparedness kit.
On Nov 4th, 2016 Randy G said
I’ve been to all the Hickory Shows for the last 2 years .. I’m a recently moved from Connecticut .. you folks who think the Hickory isn’t worth going to should take it from me .. IT’S GREAT ! Yes, I’ve been to Charlotte and it’s bigger but what is available for the buying public here in this state whether the show is big or small should be appreciated. I’ll continue to support the promoters by going .. till I’m too old to walk.
On Oct 28th, 2016 John Aronis said
I have enjoyed the gun shows in Hickory thanks
On Jan 26th, 2016 Bill said
The Hickory gun show is not worth it . Even if you manage to print of the dollar coupon, it’s still not worth paying eight dollars to go.
On May 9th, 2021 Tricia said
Totally disagree with this comment. We attend all the shows and there are tons of items at great prices.

When it Comes to Quality and Innovation
One Name Springs to Mind.
Founded in 1944, Hickory Springs has grown from a small producer of furniture springs into a leading supplier of diversified components for the bedding, furniture, and GSA industry. From flexible polyurethane foam fabrication and polyester fiber batting to formed steel wire production, Hickory Springs continues to extend its traditional product lines to include sleeper mechanisms, roll-packed mattresses, and fabric-encased micro coils. This exceptional diversification in products and processes is a core commitment to our customers in the furniture and bedding markets where Hickory Springs excels with quality products that enhance market opportunities.
From engineered innerspring frames to innovative micro coil constructions, Hickory Springs is a leading supplier to the bedding industry.
Hickory Springs specializes in the manufacturing of seating components, sleeper  mechanisms and mattresses for residential and hospitality markets including foam, fiber, and converting capabilities.
Hickory Springs can supply the quality bedding frames and sleep components you need for your institutional and government markets.
Forging, forming, bending, stamping — here’s where you can create the kind of metal components you need for frames and motion mechanisms, including incliners, recliners, rockers and swivel bases.
